Author: Tokenaire
Title: 📌 █ ANN █ PRE-ICO █ Tokenaire ░░░░░░ 2 Partnerships + 4 Tokenized Supporters ✔️
Body: Let me explain our platform based on an example: A musician called Justin tokenizes himself and sells his Justin tokens to his fans on our exchange. He can then hold polls with his token holders: “Where should I start the tour: a) London b) Berlin” Now, in London there are more fans, however, the fans in Berlin have more Justin tokens and are hence the bigger Stakeholders. Hence Berlin fans can win this poll. Big Bonus: Justin is now able to differentiate between his fans, whether they are hardcore fans or just regular followers. With our platform, he can identify them and directly reach out to his biggest token holders, for instance to market premium content.

Author: Tokenaire
Title: 📌 █ ANN █ PRE-ICO █ Tokenaire ░░░░░░ 2 Partnerships + 4 Tokenized Supporters ✔️
Body: Its the perfect blockchain for our use cases.  Advantages that made us choose Waves over Ethereum: - no custom contract needs to be added to see, receive and send them in your Wallet -> big advantage for personalized tokens  - data-transactions are super cheap in comparison to Ethereum -> our Time Capsule Feature that stores data DIRECTLY on the blockchain becomes economical (check out this experiment that does the same on Ethereum, but 1KB costs roughly 1$: https://boobies.surge.sh/)  - Faster Transactions, 5 times faster than Ethereum

Title: 📌 █ ANN █ PRE-ICO █ Tokenaire ░░░░░░ 2 Partnerships + 4 Tokenized Supporters ✔️

Granted, Ethereum is working on getting POS as well in the near future. (called Casper)

Author: Tokenaire
Title: 📌 █ ANN █ PRE-ICO █ Tokenaire ░░░░░░ 2 Partnerships + 4 Tokenized Supporters ✔️
Body: Thank you for your kind words!  The referral program works as follows: After you performed the KYC process (identity verification) successfully on your token sale account, you see a link. Share them with your friends or followers, our system tracks how much they invested, and you receive 5% of the BTC they spent directly after the token sale. The requirement is though that they spend at least 1 BTC collectively through your link.  You can already get your referral link, just sign up on our website.  Hope that helps

Author: Tokenaire
Title: 📌 █ ANN █ PRE-ICO █ Tokenaire ░░░░░░ 2 Partnerships + 4 Tokenized Supporters ✔️
Body: Hi FutureICOs and thanks for your kind words!  We facilitate a new concept called data-transactions, which makes it economical to store data directly on the blockchain. This means, unlike file storage solutions like STORJ which only store a hash of your file on the blockchain while storing the file off-chain, we store the entire data directly and immutably on the blockchain. Your data can not be lost, that is the huge advantage compared to STORJ which can only guarantee that your file was not corrupted.  You can learn more about Data Transactions here: https://docs.wavesplatform.com/technical-details/data-transaction.html
